org.sxb.convert.converter

インタフェース Converter<S,T>

  • 型パラメータ:
    S - the source type 源类型
    T - the target type 目标类型
    既知の実装クラスのリスト:
    DeserializingConverter, JedisExceptionConverter, JedisScriptReturnConverter, ListConverter, LongToBooleanConverter, MapConverter, MapToPropertiesConverter, SerializingConverter, SetConverter, StringToCharsetConverter, StringToDataTypeConverter, StringToPropertiesConverter, StringToRedisClientInfoConverter, TransactionResultConverter

    public interface Converter<S,T>
    A converter converts a source object of type S to a target of type T.
    转换源对象类型S到目标对象类型T的转换接口

    Implementations of this interface are thread-safe and can be shared.

    实现本接口的类将是线程安全并可以共享的

    Implementations may additionally implement ConditionalConverter.

    实现类可以另外实现其他接口ConditionalConverter

    導入されたバージョン:
    2.0
    作成者:
    Keith Donald, Jeffson

    • メソッドの概要

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      修飾子とタイプ メソッドと説明
      T convert(S source)
      Convert the source object of type S to target type T.

    • メソッドの詳細

      • convert

        T convert(S source)
        Convert the source object of type S to target type T.
        パラメータ:
        source - the source object to convert, which must be an instance of S (never null)
        戻り値:
        the converted object, which must be an instance of T (potentially null)
        例外:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if the source cannot be converted to the desired target type
